        <short>Caseless 5mm assault rifle.</short>
        <description>
            <para>
                Light assault rifle firing a smaller round that is still
                effective against unarmoured targets. It is very light
                and reliable, and commonly found as the principle weapon
                of first world armies, as well as in the hands of third
                world militia.
            </para>
