        <short>Caseless 7mm battle rifle.</short>
        <description>
            <para>
                A rifle designed for longer range engagements than what
                the more compact assault rifles are used for. It is
                limited to semi-automatic and 3-round burst fire, since
                fully automatic fire at greater ranges isn't viewed as
                being useful.
            </para>
